  "42 - Purge du circuit": {
   "width": 11940,
   "height": 9060,
   "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": ". Pour r\u00e9aliser la purge du circuit du bloc hydraulique et afin de ne pas introduire d'air,  il faut:",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 720,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-PHASE 1- ARG- Appuyer fortement sur la p\u00e9dale de frein et tout en maintenant la pression sur celle ci :",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,128,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 10080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Moteur coup\u00e9, apr\u00e8s 3 appuis sur la p\u00e9dale de frein, ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 960,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Installer l'appareil de purge sur le bocal de liquide frein.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Refermer le purgeur ARG et relacher la pedale si il n' y a plus d'air dans le circuit",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 3480,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8160
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- ATTENTION: Attendre 5 minutes au moins avant de relancer un cycle de purge",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,9,9)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 8760,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- S'assurer que les vis de purge (purgeur) soient ferm\u00e9es.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Ouvrir la vis de purge ARG et lancer l'ordre de purge de la roue ARG en pompant sur la pedale",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 2880,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 3960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
